asked to see him.

1063
01:13:18,227 --> 01:13:19,429
Ah!

1064
01:13:26,169 --> 01:13:29,038
If you don't mind,
I'd like a few words
with my Italian colleague.

1065
01:13:29,072 --> 01:13:30,540
Of course.

1066
01:13:32,542 --> 01:13:34,210
It was a
short meeting.

1067
01:13:34,243 --> 01:13:38,448
The Syrian Foreign minister
was caught off guard when
I told him the Achille Lauro 

