the Syrians
are not acting
in good faith?

1071
01:13:45,088 --> 01:13:47,156
We picked up
a radio message
from a Syrian base

1072
01:13:47,190 --> 01:13:49,926
ordering the ship
to head for Tartus.

1073
01:13:49,959 --> 01:13:52,962
