1074
01:13:52,996 --> 01:13:56,733
Syria cannot go
granting asylum
to those bandits.

1075
01:13:56,766 --> 01:13:58,101
Or even allow
the ship to dock.

1076
01:13:58,134 --> 01:13:59,769
I'm with
you there.

1077
01:13:59,803 --> 01:14:03,106
It is vital that no sympathy
be shown toward an action
against the innocent civilians.

1078
01:14:04,774 --> 01:14:07,076
I want you to know
we are ready to take
military action

1079
01:14:07,110 --> 01:14:09,078
in a defense of
the US citizens
held hostage.

1080
01:14:10,514 --> 01:14:12,549
I hope Italy's position
is equally firm.

1081
01:14:12,582 --> 01:14:14,183
I want you
to know,

1082
01:14:14,217 --> 01:14:17,220
if it is decided
that military action
is unavoidable,

1083
01:14:17,253 --> 01:14:19,088
the ship is Italian,
remember.

1084
01:14:19,122 --> 01:14:21,925
So any action
will be undertaken
by Italy.

1085
01:14:21,958 --> 01:14:23,493
And no one
but Italy.

1086
01:14:27,096 --> 01:14:30,133
I want you to be clear
that Italy's first concern

1087
01:14:30,166 --> 01:14:32,969
is to avoid the shedding
innocent blood.

1088
01:14:33,002 --> 01:14:35,572
And we will do all we can
to reach a peaceful solution.

1089
01:14:35,605 --> 01:14:38,107
MAN: Excuse me,
but the minister is waiting,
Your Excellency.

1090
01:14:38,141 --> 01:14:39,275
Excuse me.

1091
