1094
01:14:48,084 --> 01:14:49,085
Come in.

1095
01:14:53,289 --> 01:14:54,691
Ah, Your Excellency.

1096
01:14:55,959 --> 01:14:56,993
Please.

1097
01:14:59,763 --> 01:15:03,533
I imagine you know
the reason for my visit, sir.

1098
01:15:03,567 --> 01:15:06,202
The Achille Lauro 
is at this moment
heading for Syria.

1099
01:15:06,235 --> 01:15:08,572
Yes, so I gather
from your American colleague.

1100
01:15:08,605 --> 01:15:10,273
Why Syria?

1101
01:15:10,306 --> 01:15:13,943
Maybe they are hoping
to receive some kind
of assistance or support?

1102
01:15:13,977 --> 01:15:15,845
Exactly what is it
you are trying to say?

1103
01:15:15,879 --> 01:15:18,848
The hijackers
claim to be
PLO guerrillas.

1104
01:15:18,882 --> 01:15:21,150
And we all know
that some of the more extreme

1105
01:15:21,184 --> 01:15:23,186
Palestinian groups
are based in Syria.

1106
01:15:23,219 --> 01:15:26,956
Syria grants asylum
to her persecuted Arab brothers.

1107
01:15:26,990 --> 01:15:29,058
But I categorically
reject the suggestion

1108
01:15:29,092 --> 01:15:31,227
that my government
has anything to do
with a group

1109
01:15:31,260 --> 01:15:33,630
whose identity
we do not even know.

1110
01:15:33,663 --> 01:15:37,100
I assume your government
also disapproves
for the act of piracy,

1111
01:15:37,133 --> 01:15:39,769
performed aboard
an Italian cruise ship.

1112
01:15:39,803 --> 01:15:41,905
Of course we do.
We condemn it entirely.

1113
01:15:41,938 --> 01:15:43,139
Very good.

1114
01:15:43,172 --> 01:15:45,942
Then there will be no problem
over issuing a public statement

1115
01:15:45,975 --> 01:15:47,310
expressing
your condemnation.

1116
01:15:50,880 --> 01:15:52,682
Our President is in
Prague at the moment.

1117
01:15:53,783 --> 01:15:55,251
I will inform him
of the situation

1118
01:15:55,284 --> 01:15:57,654
and pass on the requests
of the Italian government.

1119
01:16:04,160 --> 01:16:07,897
[ARABIC MUSIC PLAYING]

1120
