will be freed.

1201
01:21:31,988 --> 01:21:33,589
We will cooperate
in every way.

1202
01:21:34,623 --> 01:21:36,092
You need
not worry.

1203
01:21:36,125 --> 01:21:37,360
Worry?

1204
01:21:37,393 --> 01:21:40,529
We do not worry.
It is you who should worry.

1205
01:21:40,563 --> 01:21:42,198
Because you
all want to live.

1206
01:21:43,499 --> 01:21:46,135
But we boarded the ship
prepared to die.

1207
01:22:19,702 --> 01:22:21,104
[YAWNING]

1208
01:22:54,770 --> 01:22:56,339
[COUGHING]

1209
01:23:05,381 --> 01:23:06,482
Leon.

1210
01:23:07,550 --> 01:23:09,185
Why don't you
try to get some rest?

1211
01:23:10,553 --> 01:23:11,720
I'm not sleepy.

1212
01:23:12,755 --> 01:23:14,490
I'm watching
our enemy.

1213
01:23:18,261 --> 01:23:20,196
They all look
so young.

1214
01:23:21,664 --> 01:23:23,699
