what he's doing?

1217
01:23:32,808 --> 01:23:35,178
You can
bet he knows.

1218
01:23:35,211 --> 01:23:37,713
He got a gun
and he knows
how to use it.

1219
01:23:42,118 --> 01:23:43,352
[SIGHS]

1220
01:23:43,386 --> 01:23:46,055
