in the newspapers.

1226
01:24:03,839 --> 01:24:06,642
And now here it is
happening to us.

1227
01:24:07,676 --> 01:24:09,178
Doesn't
seem possible.

1228
01:24:09,845 --> 01:24:11,247
[SIGHS]

1229
01:24:13,616 --> 01:24:15,218
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

1230
01:24:19,855 --> 01:24:21,357
But you know...

1231
01:24:22,891 --> 01:24:25,161
I would like
to talk to them.

1232
01:24:25,194 --> 01:24:27,596
