We're not people.

1237
01:24:47,350 --> 01:24:48,684
My dearest heart,

1238
01:24:51,420 --> 01:24:53,389
what would you know...

1239
01:24:53,422 --> 01:24:57,126
Well, if they could act
like human beings instead of...

1240
01:25:00,629 --> 01:25:02,131
I don't know...

1241
01:25:02,731 --> 01:25:04,467
It just
seems to me

1242
01:25:04,500 --> 01:25:06,635
that the world
is big enough.

1243
01:25:06,669 --> 01:25:08,804
