Hey. Hey. Hey.

1259
01:26:51,574 --> 01:26:52,575
Hey!

1260
01:27:04,287 --> 01:27:05,821
[JUBILANT MUSIC PLAYING]

1261
01:27:14,463 --> 01:27:15,764
